# ==========================================
# COMPREHENSIVE .gitignore TEMPLATE
# ==========================================
# This template covers common files and directories
# that should be ignored in most projects
#
# ⚠️  IMPORTANT: This is a TEMPLATE - customize it for your project!
# - Review each section and remove what you don't need
# - Pay special attention to lock files (usually should be committed!)
# - Check database files if you have seed data
# - Adjust based on your specific tech stack

